---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Calcverse"
  description="Terms of service for Calcverse calculator tools"
>
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="heading-lg mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="text-neutral-600">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            By accessing and using Calcverse ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
            If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Calcverse provides free online calculators for various financial and business calculations.
            Our tools are designed to help you estimate earnings, fees, and other financial metrics.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Disclaimer of Accuracy</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Important:</strong> The calculators on this site are provided for informational and
            educational purposes only. Results are estimates based on the inputs you provide and may not
            reflect actual outcomes.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Calculations are based on general formulas and may not account for all factors</li>
            <li>Platform fees, tax rates, and other variables change over time</li>
            <li>Results should not be relied upon for financial, tax, or legal decisions</li>
            <li>Always consult with qualified professionals for financial advice</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">No Financial Advice</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Nothing on this website constitutes financial, tax, legal, or professional advice.
            The information provided is general in nature and should not be used as a substitute
            for consultation with professional advisors.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Calcverse and its operators shall not be liable
            for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages resulting from:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Use or inability to use our calculators</li>
            <li>Reliance on any calculation results</li>
            <li>Errors or inaccuracies in calculations</li>
            <li>Any decisions made based on information from this site</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            All content on Calcverse, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property
            of Calcverse or its content suppliers and is protected by intellectual property laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Embedding</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            You may embed our calculators on your website using the provided embed codes.
            When embedding:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Do not modify the calculator functionality</li>
            <li>Do not remove attribution links</li>
            <li>You may not claim the calculators as your own creation</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Modifications</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the service
            after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws,
            without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about these terms, please contact us through our website.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
